ESP-NOW protocol

- secure simple pair
    - generate/exchange keys
    - encrypt using psk
- psk, pair keys, cryptography, random iv
- replay attack protection

- confirmation by central
- communication initiated by central
- documentation

Roadmap
=======

- OTA commit all or nothing
- MicroPython OTA
- MQTT with TLS
- MQTT w/o blocking points (move poll() into event loop)
- Replace polling by IRQs, callbacks, etc.
- Remote mpy console, if possible
